description:
Expand your track list with more songs from the 90's! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• Corona "Rhythm of the Night"
• Rednex "Cotton Eye Joe"
• Technotronic "Pump Up The Jam"
• The Cardigans "Lovefool"
• Gala "Freed from Desire"
name: Let's Sing - Best of 90's Vol. 2 Song Pack
